label.value: EC 2.7.1.* (phosphotransferases with an alcohol group as acceptor) inhibitor

definition.value: An EC 2.7.* (P-containing group transferase) inhibitor that interferes with the action of any phosphotransferase with an alcohol group as acceptor (EC 2.7.1.*).
